dc_title_s: Map of the city of Detroit Michigan: showing steam and electric railways and the location of the principal manufactories, etc.; drawn and published by Wm. Sauer.; Sauer's commercial pocket map of Detroit
dc_description_s: 1 map: col.; 51 x 79 cm., folded to 14 x 22 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
